here until he gets well.

106
00:07:42,770 --> 00:07:46,370
I don't know how I can help him, though.

107
00:07:47,400 --> 00:07:50,320
It was a curious turn of fate to meet you.

108
00:07:50,320 --> 00:07:51,850
I agree.

109
00:07:51,850 --> 00:07:54,020
Although we were both locked up in

110
00:07:54,020 --> 00:07:56,700
the greatest prison in the world - Impel Down,

111
00:07:56,980 --> 00:07:59,660
if it weren't for Luffy-kun,

112
00:07:59,660 --> 00:08:04,250
we would have never met each
other at all I suppose.

113
00:08:04,710 --> 00:08:11,050
We both tried really hard to keep up
with Straw boy at Marineford, didn't we?

114
00:08:11,510 --> 00:08:13,720
It's hard to say goodbye to you

115
00:08:13,720 --> 00:08:18,550
