for me to come back to the kingdom.

116
00:08:18,970 --> 00:08:22,480
Please take good care of Straw boy!

117
00:08:26,900 --> 00:08:30,440
Bye, Straw Hat! Thank you for letting us out!

118
00:08:30,440 --> 00:08:34,280
My dream can come true because of you!

119
00:08:34,280 --> 00:08:36,950
Say "hi" to him when he wakes up!

120
00:08:36,950 --> 00:08:41,120
--See you again if we have a chance!
--Hang in there!

121
00:08:41,120 --> 00:08:44,080
