144
00:10:12,540 --> 00:10:16,920
Ladies, carry Luffy to the Kuja
Castle as soon as possible!

145
00:10:17,590 --> 00:10:22,100
--I'm gonna look after Luffy...
--Wait a minute, Snake Princess!

146
00:10:24,100 --> 00:10:25,470
