00:17:37,410 --> 00:17:43,330
We promised that when he gets
well, we would invite Luffy alone.

251
00:17:43,330 --> 00:17:45,080
Wait for that moment!

252
00:17:45,080 --> 00:17:48,710
I can't! I am an empress!
Don't tell me what to do!

253
00:17:48,710 --> 00:17:49,870
I said no!

254
00:17:49,870 --> 00:17:53,090
The most important thing is
the hereditary policy of this country!

255
00:17:53,910 --> 00:17:58,430
Honestly! You're infected
by such a strong virus!

256
00:17:58,430 --> 00:18:02,470
I can't believe that the fearful
pirate empress has become love sick!

257
00:18:03,520 --> 00:18:07,560
However, he must have been like a small ant

258
00:18:07,560 --> 00:18:11,150
diving into a tempest at
Impel Down and the Navy HQ.

259
00:18:11,150 --> 00:18:15,990
It must have been an act of God to let
him live and be brought back here.

260
00:18:15,990 --> 00:18:21,160
I wonder what God expects from him.

261
00:18:22,490 --> 00:18:25,910
--Hey, pass me the wrench.
--Okay, here you go.

262
00:18:25,820 --> 00:18:28,960
Hey, do you think you can fix the ship?

263
00:18:28,960 --> 00:18:33,210
Yeah, I'll manage.  That aside,
where did Straw Hat go?

264
00:18:33,210 --> 00:18:35,150
Jimbei is gone, too.

265
00:18:35,150 --> 00:18:37,120
I don't know.

266
00:18:38,480 --> 00:18:41,670
Well, I heard that if a man enters the

267
00:18:41,670 --> 00:18:44,090
Maiden Island, he's gonna be turned to stone

268
00:18:44,090 --> 00:18:46,220
but maybe it's worth dying for.

269
00:18:46,220 --> 00:18:51,520
According to Aphelandra-chan, not
all women were there at the port.

270
00:18:51,520 --> 00:18:56,530
The female-only island that I dreamed
of! I wish I could take a look inside!

271
00:18:56,530 --> 00:18:58,650
You're gonna die, you idiot.

272
00:18:58,650 --> 00:19:00,740
I wonder if there are female bears...

273
00:19:00,740 --> 00:19:02,540
It's Maiden Island!

274
00:19:02,540 --> 00:19:03,800
I'm sorry.

275
00:19:03,800 --> 00:19:06,610
Only humans! There are only humans!

276
00:19:06,610 --> 00:19:08,640
I'm really sorry!

277
00:19:52,600 --> 00:19:55,210
Where am I?

278
00:19:56,740 --> 00:20:00,010
Maybe it was all a dream...

279
00:20:15,260 --> 00:20:18,860
I'm sorry, Luffy...

280
00:20:22,660 --> 00:20:25,840
I couldn't make it all the way.

281
00:20:36,220 --> 00:20:39,250
Go away! Go away!

282
00:20:39,250 --> 00:20:40,630
Luffy!

283
00:20:41,880 --> 00:20:44,590
No!

284
00:20:51,020 --> 00:20:55,700
Go away! Go away!

285
00:21:33,710 --> 00:21:36,440
If I don't escape death...

286
00:21:37,580 --> 00:21:42,230
I'm sorry but could you
look after my brother?

287
00:21:44,620 --> 00:21:47,310
The war is over!

288
00:21:47,310 --> 00:21:48,820
Ace-san is...

289
00:21:49,130 --> 00:21:52,160
Don't say it! Don't say anything!

290
00:21:53,530 --> 00:21:58,360
I already pinched myself
hard enough to rip my skin!

291
00:22:01,030 --> 00:22:03,170
If it were a dream, I should've woken by now!

292
00:22:05,660 --> 00:22:08,050
It's not a dream, is it?

293
00:22:16,890 --> 00:22:20,980
Ace is really dead, isn't he?!

294
00:22:27,840 --> 00:22:30,590
Yes, he is dead!

295
00:22:38,780 --> 00:22:42,020
Hey grandpa, who is Ace?

296
00:22:42,020 --> 00:22:44,630
Oh, he is...

297
00:22:45,210 --> 00:22:49,380
...the guy who will become your brother!

298
00:22:50,340 --> 00:22:55,220
Luffy! I'll see you at the
top of the pirates' world!

299
00:22:55,680 --> 00:22:57,870
Come to the top!

300
00:23:13,740 --> 00:23:17,920
Ace!!

301
00:23:25,320 --> 00:23:27,840
Next week is a special
collaboration with Toriko!

302
00:23:27,840 --> 00:23:29,590
Those Barbecue Pigs are scary!

303
00:23:29,590 --> 00:23:31,520
Whew, I'm stuffed! That was tasty!

304
00:23:31,520 --> 00:23:33,820
Apparently there are lots
more of these things!

305
00:23:33,820 --> 00:23:34,680
Really?!

306
00:23:34,680 --> 00:23:37,170
That's what Toriko said! I wanna go home!

307
00:23:37,170 --> 00:23:39,100
Okay! We're going with Toriko!

308
00:23:39,100 --> 00:23:40,310
What?!

309
00:23:40,310 --> 00:23:42,850
Next week, the special Toriko x
One Piece collaboration episode!

310
00:23:42,850 --> 00:23:45,750
"The Strongest Tag-Team! Luffy
and Toriko's Hard Struggle!"

311
00:23:45,750 --> 00:23:47,220
Don't miss it!
